name: Vegas Rules EP
description:
The brand new 5 track EP from Preston Pop Punkers "Better Left Alone"

Vegas Rules see the band teaming up again with The Outhouse Studio in Reading to record an EP that is still Pop Punk but with a more mature edge. This sophomore release is sure to please old and new fans alike. 

This is a Pop Punk journey you're not going to want to miss and hope you're all on board for the ride.

Tracklisting:

1. Chinese Whispers
2. Echoes
3. Going For The Oscar
4. Ambition (A Vision)
5. In The Crowd

name: Better Left Alone EP

The brand new EP from Better Left Alone is finally here!

Featuring 5 new tracks, this is Better Left Alone as you have never heard them before!

Recorded with John Mitchell @ The Outhouse Studios in Reading in August of 2010, don't miss out on owning this limited run of the new EP

Tracklisting:

2. Wanna Talk?
3. Move Forward
4. Positives
5. We Will Never Know
